Sappi Expects to Cut More Jobs Across Operations in Fiscal 2012, CEO Says

-- B y   J a n i c e   K e w
-- 
2011-08-04T08:44:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/sappi-expects-to-cut-more-jobs-across-operations-in-fiscal-2012-ceo-says.html
Sappi Ltd. (SAP)  the world’s largest
producer of coated fine paper, expects more job losses across
its operations in fiscal 2012, Chief Executive Officer Ralph
Boettger said.  “Unfortunately, there will be job losses in the new fiscal
year across our global businesses” as part of efforts to
further reduce costs, he said in a telephone interview from
Johannesburg today, declining specify how many employees could
lose their positions.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Janice Kew in Johannesburg at 
